name: hoshinplan
description: Hoshinplan is a tool to make it easy for companies to share and track their strategy.
full_description:
Ruby on Rails application to share and track company strategy.

Hoshinplan.com uses three container types to run: `web`, `worker` and `clock`. You can start them by running:
```bash
/start [type]
```


We have a hosted version of the tool at https://www.hoshinplan.com

You can get the source code at https://github.com/gabriprat/hoshinplan
